Description: Clipboard auto-trimmer tray app for KDE Plasma
 Trimmeh KDE trims multi-line shell snippets on the clipboard into single-line commands.

Package: trimmeh-cli
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Command-line interface for Trimmeh
 Trimmeh CLI provides trim and diff commands for shell snippets.
